PSCT.Base: When a Link Monster's effect is activated that targets this face-up card on the field (Quick Effect): You can destroy this card, then destroy 1 monster in the column this card was in, and if you do, destroy any monsters in that card's adjacent zones. You can only use each effect of "Shelrokket Dragon" once per turn.
